  function calculateNumericCells() {
    calculatedNumericCells.forEach(function(calculatedNumericCell) {
      calculateNumericCell(calculatedNumericCell.id);
    });
  }

  function calculateCheckboxCells() {
    calculatedCheckboxCells.forEach(function(calculatedCheckboxCell) {
      calculateCheckboxCell(calculatedCheckboxCell.id);
    });
  }

  function calculateNumericCell(inputId) {
    var total = 0;

    var calculateNumericCell = calculatedNumericCells.find(function(cell) {
      return cell.id == inputId;
    });

    calculateNumericCell.children.forEach(function(childId) {
      var value = $("#" + childId).val();

      if (value != "" && !isNaN(value)) {
        total = total + parseInt(value);
      }
    });

    $("#" + inputId).val(total);
    $("#" + inputId).trigger("change");
  }

  function calculateCheckboxCell(inputId) {
    var isChecked = false;

    var calculateCheckboxCell = calculatedCheckboxCells.find(function(cell) {
      return cell.id == inputId;
    });

    calculateCheckboxCell.children.forEach(function(childId) {
      var childIsChecked = $("#" + childId).is(":checked");

      if (childIsChecked == true) {
        isChecked = true;
      }
    });

    $("#" + inputId).prop("checked", isChecked);
  }

  function onNumericInputChange(changedInputId) {
    calculatedNumericCells.forEach(function(calculatedNumericCell) {
      calculatedNumericCell.children.forEach(function(childId) {
        if (changedInputId == childId) {
          calculateNumericCell(calculatedNumericCell.id);
          return;
        }
      });
    });
  }

  function onCheckboxInputChange(changedInputId) {
    calculatedCheckboxCells.forEach(function(calculatedCheckboxCell) {
      calculatedCheckboxCell.children.forEach(function(childId) {
        if (changedInputId == childId) {
          calculateCheckboxCell(calculatedCheckboxCell.id);
          return;
        }
      });
    });
  }

  function append(tab, i, value) {
    $(
      "#" +
        tab +
        " div#cde table tbody tr:nth-child(" +
        (i + 1) +
        ") th:nth-child(3)"
    ).empty();
    $(
      "#" +
        tab +
        " div#cde table tbody tr:nth-child(" +
        (i + 1) +
        ") th:nth-child(3)"
    ).append(value);
  }

  function get_resource_link(element_id, tokens) {
    $.ajax({
      url: "../api/documents",
      type: "get",
      data: {
        fields: 'id',
        filter: 'name:token:'+tokens
      },
      success: function(response) {
        id = response['documents'][0]['id'];
        document.getElementById(element_id).href= '../api/documents/'+ id + '/data'
      },
      error: function(xhr) {
        console.log("Error in the request");
        console.log(xhr);
      }
    });
  }

  $(document).ready(function() {
    $(function() {
      //alert("Here")
      $("#mod2_tabs").tabs({
        activate: function(event, ui) {
          $("#tab0 div#cde table tbody tr th:nth-child(3) input").each(function(

            append("tab1", i, row.value);

            append("tab4", i, row.value);
          });
        }
      });

      $(".read-only input").each(function() {
        $(this).attr("disabled", "disabled");
      });

      $("input[type=text]").on("input", function(e) {
        onNumericInputChange(e.target.id);
      });
      $("input[type=checkbox]").on("change", function(e) {
        onCheckboxInputChange(e.target.id);
      });
    });

    $(function() {
      console.log('Updating file resources links')
      get_resource_link('handbook_link', 'NHWA, Indicator, HandBook');
      get_resource_link('userguide_link', 'NHWA, User, guide');
      get_resource_link('occupation_link', 'NHWA, Occupation, Mapping');
    })
  });
  var expanded = false;

  function showCheckboxes(element) {
    var checkboxes = document.getElementById(element);
    //var checkboxes = element.id;
    if (!expanded) {
      checkboxes.style.display = "block";
      expanded = true;
    } else {
      checkboxes.style.display = "none";
      expanded = false;
    }
  }

  $(this).on(dhis2.de.event.dataValuesLoaded, function() {
    values.forEach(function(value) {
      $("#" + value.id + "-Xr12mI7VPn3-val").on("change", function() {
        $("#alert-error").hide();
      });
    });

    if ($("#newCompleteButton").length == 0) {
      $("#newCompleteButton").removeAttr("disabled");
      var inn = "input";
      $("<" + inn + ">")
        .attr({
          type: "button",
          id: "newCompleteButton",
          name: "newCompleteButton",
          value: "Complete",
          onclick: "complete()",
          style: "width:120px;display:none"
        })
        .prependTo("#completenessDiv");
    }
    var interval = setInterval(function() {
      if ($("#undoButton").length != 0) {
        if (
          $("#undoButton").attr("disabled") == undefined ||
          $("#undoButton").attr("disabled") == ""
        ) {
          $("#newCompleteButton").attr("disabled", "disabled");
        } else {
          $("#newCompleteButton").removeAttr("disabled");
        }
        clearInterval(interval);
      }
    }, 100);

    calculateNumericCells();
    calculateCheckboxCells();
  });

  dhis2.util.on("dhis2.de.event.completed", function(event, ds) {
    $("#newCompleteButton").attr("disabled", "disabled");
  });
  dhis2.util.on("dhis2.de.event.uncompleted", function(event, ds) {
    $("#newCompleteButton").removeAttr("disabled");
  });
  $("#alert-error").hide();
  function complete() {
    registerCompleteDataSet();
  }

  function updateWarningsSourceTypes(row) {
    const inputFields = Array.from(row.querySelectorAll("input.entryfield"));
    const checkboxes = Array.from(row.querySelectorAll("input.entrytrueonly"));
    const checkboxTd = row.querySelector("td:last-child");
    const inputsAreTotals = inputFields.reduce(
      (acc, field) => field.disabled === true || acc,
      false
    );
    const inputsHaveValue = inputFields.reduce(
      (acc, field) => field.value !== "" || acc,
      false
    );
    const checkboxesHaveValue = checkboxes.reduce(
      (acc, checkbox) => $(`#${checkbox.id}`).prop("checked") || acc,
      false
    );

    if (inputsHaveValue && !checkboxesHaveValue && !inputsAreTotals) {
      checkboxTd.style.backgroundColor = "#fcbeb6";
    } else {
      checkboxTd.style.backgroundColor = "transparent";
    }
  }

  $("table.withSourceType").on("change", "input", function() {
    var row = $(this).closest("table.withSourceType > tbody > tr")[0];
    updateWarningsSourceTypes(row);
  });

  function loadWarningsSourceTypes() {
    $("table.withSourceType > tbody > tr").each(function(idx, row) {
      updateWarningsSourceTypes(row);
    });
  }

  loadWarningsSourceTypes();
  $(this).on(dhis2.de.event.dataValuesLoaded, loadWarningsSourceTypes);
</script>
